render MQ Summary.

Source: R/vignetteHelpers.R
render_MQSummary_rmd.Rd

render MQ Summary.

render_MQSummary_rmd(
  pdata,
  config,
  pep = TRUE,
  dest_path = ".",
  dest_file_name = "MQSummary2",
  workdir = tempdir(),
  format = c("pdf", "html")
)

Arguments

pdata

data.frame
config

AnalysisConfiguration

See also

Other vignetteHelpers: INTERNAL_FUNCTIONS_BY_FAMILY, render_SummarizeFiltering_rmd()

Examples

bb <- LFQServiceData::skylinePRMSampleData_A
config <- bb$config_f()
analysis <- bb$analysis(bb$data, bb$config_f())

#> creating sampleName
#> completing cases
render_MQSummary_rmd(analysis,
  config , workdir= ".")# tempdir(check = FALSE))
